Zombie pirates are encountered during Rum Deal on Braindeath Island (level 50), during The Great Brain Robbery on Harmony Island (level 49) and during Pieces of Hate on Mos Le'Harmless (Level 35). They are aggressive creatures in both locations. It is not recommended to train on them, unless you want to attain free herbs/runes. These are one of the only creatures to regularly drop bandana and eyepatches.

Although the ones' on Braindeath Island weakness is air spells when not attacked, it changes to crushing attacks when in combat.
